type: article
title: "A Canonical Quaternionic Intermediate Representation for Single-Qubit Quantum Circuits"
version: "0.1.0"
abstract: "This paper defines a canonical quaternionic intermediate representation for single-qubit circuit segments and specifies deterministic normalization, sign canonicalization, and segment-fusion rules for single-qubit gate action modulo global phase."
